sequenceDiagram
    participant MO as BO User / MO
    participant BO as BO (Integration API)
    participant SNS as SNS / EventBridge
    participant SQS as SQS (BOSI Queue)
    participant BOSI as BOSI Service
    participant SI as S&I Platform

    MO->>BO: Change interest rate on credit
    BO->>BO: Process mutation<br/>+ calculate new premium
    BO->>SNS: credit.mutated event
    SNS->>SQS: Route to BOSI queue
    SQS->>BOSI: Consume event
    Note over BOSI: Mutation Orchestrator
    BOSI->>BO: GET /api/v2/loans/{creditId}
    BO-->>BOSI: Updated credit details (incl. premium)
    BOSI->>BO: GET /api/v2/related-products/{rpId}
    BO-->>BOSI: S&I account details
    Note over BOSI: Transform mutation data
    BOSI->>SI: PUT /accounts/{siAccountId}
    SI-->>BOSI: 200 OK
    Note over SQS: Delete message (ack)
